game.name: Monoa City Parking
game.description:
Parking cars at the defined places requires full control on car driving and the arrow keys. Do you want to test your car parking abilities? Join Monoa City Parking and be prepared to park your chosen vehicle at a specific location within the limited time period! Common boys! You would have a full city to explore in this brand new racing game. Try to complete each challenge before the time runs out otherwise you will lose!

The top area of the screen will guide you about how to reach the parking place before the time is running out. Track the clock on the top left corner of the screen! Be careful as there are multiple levels will be there to slow your car down in this HTML5 car parking game! Try not to hit any obstacles you see on the road and keep your eyes on collecting as much money as possible till your complete your level! Use that cash to upgrade your vehicle to make your gameplay more interesting!

Unlock new cars with the money you collect by parking your vehicle successfully in this cool racing game! You would be guided for the right direction through the red arrows shown on the screen. Be attentive since not each level coms with the same difficulties! Fasten your seat belt and drive your car properly to enjoy a successful parking experience in multiple levels! You can play this free car game on multiple devices including mobile phones, no download required.
